title.narrative: Enhanced local capacity to develop and operationalise IECD centered, equitable and inclusive high impact child survival and development packages in focus provinces

description.narrative: The IECD model is progressing well in each of the 27 project communes in nine districts of the three project provinces (Dien Bien, Gia Lai and Kon Tum). Comprehensive interventions on EENC, nutrition and water and sanitation were delivered as part of the IECD service package, including early learning and early stimulation practices. New services to address acute malnutrition were provided in six out of 27 project communes, and 37,963 parents/care givers were reached with new knowledge and skills on IECD care. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
